{"tid":1793890,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[埋大] group project 最怕豬隊友","createTime":"2019-12-22T17:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T00:05:51.000Z","uid":25570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b234f874687863226355bd0b4e819c6ddab18ea3","tid":1793890,"uid":25570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:19:55.000Z","msg":"埋大今個sem 有得揀淨係show pass/fail<br />\n個teammate apply 左<br />\n但我mid term 考得好,無理由apply<br />\n之後就仆街喇<br />\n<br />\n條友hea 到一個點<br />\n如果佢係前線手足<br />\n主動比佢做free-rider 都完全無問題<br />\n但佢唔撚係,去到呢個時勢都仲係港豬一隻<br />\n而家屌佢又唔係<br />\n唔屌佢又真係死肚氣<br />\n<br />\nd 野做到1/4咁，唔湯唔水<br />\nd code 打到一半,normalize 完d data出左result<br />\n又唔撚denormalize 個result<br />\ndel 晒又唔係,唔del 又唔係<br />\n我都唔知應該點撚樣處置佢<br />\n叫佢再follow 下,補番d 要做既野<br />\n又唔撚應機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b909310450f370104d26a26fddbf9098c94d6c2a","tid":1793890,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:27:05.000Z","msg":"有冇攞個鍵盤屌尻佢?"},{"pid":"0cadb8f4b9107661048aafaf0909b4d503c44f33","tid":1793890,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"幾時deadline先?"},{"pid":"bff545a42d25dd9062c9f62b145acbc8bf60262b","tid":1793890,"uid":62167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"groupmate自己簡 仆街唔好喊<br />\n做錯決定當然要負責<br />\n揀錯groupmate最多衰一個sem<br />\n結錯婚可能會畀人分一半身家<br />\n經一事蔡一智"},{"pid":"c8c60e3841de22726ffc99d4548ad7ec89b51dcd","tid":1793890,"uid":25570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bff545a42d25dd9062c9f62b145acbc8bf60262b","tid":1793890,"uid":62167,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"groupmate自己簡 仆街唔好喊<br />\n做